description: Creates an Amazon SageMaker Model Card export job.

parameters.name: ModelCardName
parameters.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card to export.

parameters.name: ModelCardExportJobName
parameters.description: The name of the model card export job.

parameters.name: OutputConfig
parameters.description: The model card output configuration that specifies the Amazon S3 path for exporting. The Amazon S3 output path to export your model card PDF.

nested_params.name: S3OutputPath
nested_params.description: The Amazon S3 output path to export your model card PDF.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card export job.
